<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { background: white; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .invoice-details { background: #fef2f2; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #dc2626; }
    .button { background: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Payment Overdue</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @user.name || @user.email_address %>,</p>
      
      <p><strong>Your RepuTable invoice is now overdue.</strong> Please make payment immediately to avoid service interruption.</p>
      
      <div class="invoice-details">
        <h3>Overdue Invoice</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Invoice Number:</strong> <%= @invoice.number %></li>
          <li><strong>Amount:</strong> <%= @invoice.amount_formatted %></li>
          <li><strong>Original Due Date:</strong> <%= @invoice.due_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
          <li><strong>Days Overdue:</strong> <%= @invoice.days_overdue %></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>Important:</strong> Your account will be suspended if payment is not received within 7 days of the due date.</p>
      
      <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.routes.url_helpers.billing_invoice_url(@invoice, host: 'reputable.co') %>" class="button">
          Pay Now
        </a>
      </p>
      
      <p>If you've already made payment, please upload your payment receipt in your account.</p>
      
      <p>Contact us immediately if you have any questions or concerns.</p>
      
      <p>Thanks,<br>
      The RepuTable Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>RepuTable - Reputation Management Made Simple</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>